**Overloading unary `operator &`** Overloading the unary `operator &` operator
is deprecated. [*Note:* Using the builtin unary `operator &` is not deprecated
&mdash; *end note*].
[*Example:*
```cpp
struct X {
  Z* operator & () const; // deprecated
};
X x;
Z* z = &x;                // deprecated

struct Y { };
Y y;
Y* w = &y;                // Not deprecated
```
